author: olegk
msg: - HttpEntity#writeTo no longer returns a boolean value

author: rooneg
msg: Stop trying to link against GDBM by default due to concerns about license.
(APU_CHECK_DBM): Don't try to search for and link against GDBM unless
the user asks us to by passing --with-gdbm.
